{"tid":651704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[亮劍］中國商務部：續對美日歐盟進口相紙徵收反傾銷稅","createTime":"2018-05-03T09:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T13:21:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1c51203678cc599ebf627ac7aa5ac6c3390fdac2","tid":651704,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180503/photo/bkncn-20180503171748389-0503_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180503171833\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180503%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180503171748389-0503_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180503171833&h=761fb82d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特使、財政部長姆紐欽周四（3日）率團訪華兩天，與中方商討貿易問題之際，中國商務部周四（3日）在發布公告，稱自今年3月23日起，對原產於美國、歐盟和日本的進口相紙繼續徵收反傾銷稅，實施期限為5年。 <br />\n<br />\n公告稱，根據商務部的2012年第10號公告，決定自2012年3月23日起，對原產於美國、歐盟和日本的進口相紙徵收反傾銷稅，實施期限為5年。如果終止反傾銷措施，有關進口相紙對中國的傾銷可能繼續或再度發生，對中國國內產業造成損害。 <br />\n<br />\n前年6月29日，商務部發布2016年第25號公告，決定即日起將富士膠片製造（歐洲）有限公司所適用的相紙反傾銷稅稅率調整為23.5%，另富士膠片製造（美國）有限公司所適用的相紙反傾銷稅稅率調整為23.6%<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180503/bkncn-20180503171748389-0503_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180503%2Fbkncn-20180503171748389-0503_05011_001.html&d=7EB62gZsKTrwMWa9SY97DF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=9d7775c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180503/bkncn-20180503171748389-0503_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"53dae84b1dfe8f02fc70c66518b14247724f4705","tid":651704,"uid":67468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T09:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3c78a91f82617c18da45d8e9d63d7a53c1a798","tid":651704,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T10:06:56.000Z","msg":"人地打你一拳<br />\n你用手指彈人地一下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />